:17:48.000Z","msg":"緊係唔得啦，一開始既電阻係大過你個廳。咁連一開始既電阻都整唔到，唔好話電腦，連ic都冇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"如果共有人類係咁細其他動物冇變<br />\n原始時代已經玩撚完啦,冇肉食冇獸皮著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皮都勇強可以小小地咁切落黎走人<br />\n肉真係得自然死既動物可以食<br />\n咁已經好難發展出部落<br />\n起到部落是但一隻動物踩一腳就陷家產"},{"pid":"12bfb3de241f49f5e43be307274468a58e4a49e1","tid":1179230,"uid":109538,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"係科技上，如電子設備本身係有物理極限，人類細d都唔會衝破到。如果整唔到電腦或CPU,我相信佢地一樣去唔到現有科技嘅程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845ee76eeed074c4ed3a1d2241453782531d6843","tid":1179230,"uid":17322,"like":12,"dislike":56,"score":-44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3029137500ea2791dd1351a492fa5e9aae93b48","tid":1179230,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"咁撚多如果？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2154153d25761a513b66b63f49d3139406354ef","tid":1179230,"uid":249885,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"f3029137500ea2791dd1351a492fa5e9aae93b48","tid":1179230,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"咁撚多如果？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80aa3509ddbd99950e473bc0ebdf616dd6cbe5d","tid":1179230,"uid":26106,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a61711f92a74d2550f70ddce19c43a23cdd6999f","tid":1179230,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"假設人類係一種好似螞蟻咁大隻嘅高智慧生物 一樣識講野，有靈活嘅手腳，仲會唔會發展到高水平文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.想問下工程巴打， 如果我地住緊嘅高樓大廈變到好似售樓模型咁細，仲可唔可以整到現有照明，電力，排污設施？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.我地現有嘅工具有無物理上嘅體質限制？ 縮小左嘅人手腳照計會靈活左，可唔可以整到啱佢地size 嘅電器/電子產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> eg 迷你冷氣，迷你iPhone 迷你雪櫃 迷你車咁？<br />\n希望識電子/mechan 嘅巴打可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.個迷你文明承唔承受到天然災害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會有震微風吹埋嚟已經好似十號風球咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁遇著真正我地本身認知嘅十號風球係喺會冚球鏟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個文明係fail 嘅話係咪證明有腦都無用 本身嘅體型都好重要？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:09:31.000Z","msg":"唔可以 <br />\n一個暴雨<br />\n咩都無撚哂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a917e1a1923121d7a8eaf2bd43bcef824dc14b","tid":1179230,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9132acdb386ee3098b568376787191816d9539ab","tid":1179230,"uid":10249,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"歐美品種可以 支那品種一定唔得"},{"pid":"1b2011b936e8716c14b1ebe5f8f6700bdee439c3","tid":1179230,"uid":38684,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"除咗人體因為水張力既限制<br />\n我諗其實科技上既野係克服到<br />\n雖然科技用品係過唔到某個體積限制<br />\n但係應該都可以發展到出黎<br />\n但可能係由更多人一齊用<br />\n因為咁大相對體積既野佔用既空間<br />\n使用既資源比例<br />\n都係催使更多人用同一個物件<br />\n就好似以前大型投石車咁<br />\n<br />\n再加上<br />\n人體積縮小<br />\n面對咁多既環境挑戰同天敵<br />\n更加需要集體合作<br />\n<br />\n我估人類文明會更加接近集體 / 軍國主義"},{"pid":"03779d0d538b7ecd81ee210694d32b757127c531","tid":1179230,"uid":5929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"我既諗法係<br />\n例如 CPU咁<br />\n電子野  人類呢家仲改進緊佢個SIZE<br />\n如果人係咁細粒<br />\n起步已經要有一定技術 所以應該好難"},{"pid":"8f87427ff94d0959dd5531a197f2d72b9899ca98","tid":1179230,"uid":33749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T21:31:01.000Z","msg":"恆溫動物太細隻嘅話<br />\n熱量散失得太快，要食好多嘢先得"},{"pid":"776afcabac2652fa55275452f6ed8e8fa629e344","tid":1179230,"uid":33749,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T21:35:26.000Z","msg":"有個節目叫size matter，大小科學<br />\n有講到人類變大縮細要面對嘅問題，主要係生理物理上<br />\n同樓主講嘅方向有唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a494f2a62ac0f2fa61bcb2e4aabcf3757959b9","tid":1179230,"uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03779d0d538b7ecd81ee210694d32b757127c531","tid":1179230,"uid":5929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"我既諗法係<br />\n例如 CPU咁<br />\n電子野  人類呢家仲改進緊佢個SIZE<br />\n如果人係咁細粒<br />\n起步已經要有一定技術 所以應該好難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:02:29.000Z","msg":"依家思路係用納米技術整到有咁細得咁細<br />\n好難想像本身一開波就發明到納米size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993d03c8d5dfd1b9f358491f634bd99588cd289e","tid":1179230,"uid":171277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時全部動物都係天敵"},{"pid":"43fd82ee4acdb362358c9ff735d3b5d2aad71c27","tid":1179230,"uid":38703,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:30:30.000Z","msg":"剩係一隻甴曱都滅一條村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b9b35dafe4324801a16b423f4be2f18c95aeb6","tid":1179230,"uid":101968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"993d03c8d5dfd1b9f358491f634bd99588cd289e","tid":1179230,"uid":171277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時全部動物都係天敵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:42:15.000Z","msg":"跟住發覺人類其實係廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5263a3b22ac2904648e3b65fae0fa8e2971bbd8","tid":1179230,"uid":183898,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"aea0ffeebc4dd403749305c67a57f946e46ba281","tid":1179230,"uid":22566,"like":615,"dislike":7,"score":608,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"大膽啲諗 依家會唔會已經係呢個情況"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:50:16.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係，可能螞蟻本身都以為自己好大隻，有自己既文明，而人本身都係咁諗，大家都察覺唔到高於自己文明既存在。"},{"pid":"0709e4533e5b37c218980693f5312669c52b84d7","tid":1179230,"uid":91094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:53:01.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過對於成個宇宙，人類連蟻都不如。<br />\n<br />\n文明一定會有，只係發展出唔同既文明"},{"pid":"0c9f878a55bbcf0e99b7e4fa4423decdb88711d4","tid":1179230,"uid":76951,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:04:53.000Z","msg":"好有趣既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到好多野<br />\n不過第一段既假設有d問題<br />\n<br />\n首先係人類既智慧<br />\n我地人類有咁既智能，係因為有咁上下大細既腦袋<br />\n入面有<span style=\"color: red;\">足夠多</span>既腦細胞裝住好多野，可以記憶，同埋引發思考同創意<br />\n所以就咁睇，如果縮到蟻咁細，好似冇乜可能有d乜智慧可言<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果有「靈魂」依樣野<br />\n智慧，思考 同腦細胞唔相關，咁就唔同講法了<br />\n會唔會可以將一個有智慧既生命既意識獨立咁放係一粒原子到呢？<br />\n<br />\n忽略上面既問題，假設真係有一個蟻咁大細既智慧生物<br />\n科技唔會先進得去邊<br />\n對於文明同科技發展，有一個非常致命既問題<br />\n蟻既大小限制左好多野<br />\n以近100年科技發展為例，佢地點樣做到一部電腦？<br />\n最初發明電腦，幾間房咁大既電腦已經係當時科技既極限<br />\n要再突破到nano tech，先整到愈來愈細，但運算能力愈來愈強既電腦<br />\n蟻人文明想發明電腦，一定經過同人類一樣既障礙：第一個具運算能力既巨型電腦<br />\n但似乎第一步都難以跨越，由材料收集，到建造<br />\n納米科技係建基於精細既電子儀器，而電子儀器係由更體積更大既儀器發展而成<br />\n人類既科技發展係由「大」去「小」，粗糙去精細<br />\n蟻咁大既人類並唔會因為體型細，而對佢地既科技發展有得益<br />\n<br />\n仲涉及好多野<br />\n總括黎講，係冇乜可能有蟻咁大既智慧生物"},{"pid":"82de4f4b15827047a9ff966699c3ad64c61d0e08","tid":1179230,"uid":196625,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:06:42.000Z","msg":"人類可以發展到文明, 主要係因為食指同姆指可以合成一個圈, 容易拎得起野發力, 而做到工具<br />\n<br />\n猩猩同馬騮做唔到, 食指太長, 所以先冇文明, 同大小唔太關係"},{"pid":"ae70957d85bc924bdd33aad213b2bc3571255289","tid":1179230,"uid":20535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:08:14.000Z","msg":"你純粹講人變細，無詳細講埋其他假設好難討論，<br />\n如果你假設其他物理常數不變，同其他生物不變，我諗人類會建立到文明，不過廢好多"},{"pid":"631be92375f636cf7c1a5b49e2df92f47f309d8d","tid":1179230,"uid":217954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T23:10:21.000Z","msg":"咁細既話，太多天敵<br />\n長期做糧食"},{"pid":"06981f22edebb25b09b8025af0dd9d6aac6a1be4","tid":1179230,"uid":29099,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:12:21.000Z","msg":"文明其中有個里程碑係鐵，如果人太細粒，但地面厚度冇變，想採礦應該難好多"},{"pid":"757d09018638c09b7998f8f34e58372dc0cff550","tid":1179230,"uid":224095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:22:19.000Z","msg":"樓主冇讀過科學化學？"},{"pid":"04be5df206bedd357195c75eec04daf5068e0094","tid":1179230,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:25:34.000Z","msg":"你以為自己好大隻?<br />\n睇過MIB未<br />\n雖然好似誇張左<br />\nbut who knows?"},{"pid":"7117d4be805170e9096a164eba7e7c6b4212c9da","tid":1179230,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"人變細，分子keep住個size，冇可能"},{"pid":"2ca7fbbe9c303dfc2fbe18231fc2eb2661ee22fa","tid":1179230,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:29:11.000Z","msg":"蟻多嬲死象"},{"pid":"90944084f8ee27f3fdab2ae36a60aeb0ae5b94e3","tid":1179230,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:30:17.000Z","msg":"太多天敵，應該發展唔到<img 