該咩都做唔到<br />\n煤，石油嗰啲"},{"pid":"3b8b057ea91e149a1981b9d8ff6fc61ca1ad8119","tid":1179230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:06:45.000Z","msg":"人類直立行走有雙手<br />\n做到複雜工具<br />\n先建立文明"},{"pid":"9f75052b99229a6465142e262b03422022f8f225","tid":1179230,"uid":148585,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"好多人直接將人變做螞蟻<br />\n螞蟻會成功就唔會係而家既螞蟻啦<br />\n<br />\n如果單純講人類既size變細 我覺得可以 反正所有野都係起出黎<br />\n大把動物可以一野咬死人類 咪一樣被人類捉住坐動物園同玩到絕種"},{"pid":"68e9bece88f79b5e3c8c889a6e81ab0590f76fa3","tid":1179230,"uid":225347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:10:48.000Z","msg":"答你1，講水，水有張力，出現喺你面前嘅水形態就好似一舊一立方米嘅布甸，排污同水喉野會絕對唔同而家"},{"pid":"a37f2200b36344ce7b6e7bdbde51a7bd1d854d03","tid":1179230,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc5d255f209cd655eecf646399c5372fb45104b3","tid":1179230,"uid":209432,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"如果生理結構不變   淨係縮到螞蟻咁細<br />\n人類連文明都嚟唔切發展就已經死清光"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:11:19.000Z","msg":"人類變細根本冇生物單挑係會打得贏"},{"pid":"2b4f42b662e625383cec5c645c675ad2f7366544","tid":1179230,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"但係咁 細隻嘅生物換黎繁殖力強<br />\n人類又冇 又唔似蟻可以浮係水面<br />\n基本上一場雨已經收皮"},{"pid":"9b82e29795e5e8a049bb2a5dbfb897f2b448f5f8","tid":1179230,"uid":22288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:11:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26b536864a705b9d7c5eacea9c34995b5965f72d","tid":1179230,"uid":149212,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"首先生理上人類已經唔可以好似螞蟻咁細<br />\n當構成人類有一億個分子 縮細100倍唔係一億個分子縮細 而係數量直接除100<br />\n屆時生理結構已經無可能一樣<br />\n<br />\n當生理問題解決 環境因素會荷克好多 同樣生理構造 人類未必可以生存到"},{"pid":"f88fdc6abdbdf9b0871bd42eca46b9d64e31d1ad","tid":1179230,"uid":148599,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"accaba6aff34f036c812b63d6784c577d973053e","tid":1179230,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"quote":{"pid":"08e044ecb01a408a8d0ab7c582f34bd08477ab3b","tid":1179230,"uid":154585,"like":162,"dislike":1,"score":161,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"水嘅張力會令到咁細嘅生物發展唔到好似人咁嘅複雜結構"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"所以你當個個都antman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"你用Marvel呢啲吹水野比，已經唔洗討論的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743251a41a7963eae6b40b6531481658785390fb","tid":1179230,"uid":18319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"普通黃雨都變天災"},{"pid":"0218a7d07ce98cb67796f53c128d7d4c5c10b767","tid":1179230,"uid":9633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a61711f92a74d2550f70ddce19c43a23cdd6999f","tid":1179230,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"假設人類係一種好似螞蟻咁大隻嘅高智慧生物 一樣識講野，有靈活嘅手腳，仲會唔會發展到高水平文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.想問下工程巴打， 如果我地住緊嘅高樓大廈變到好似售樓模型咁細，仲可唔可以整到現有照明，電力，排污設施？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.我地現有嘅工具有無物理上嘅體質限制？ 縮小左嘅人手腳照計會靈活左，可唔可以整到啱佢地size 嘅電器/電子產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> eg 迷你冷氣，迷你iPhone 迷你雪櫃 迷你車咁？<br />\n希望識電子/mechan 嘅巴打可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.個迷你文明承唔承受到天然災害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會有震微風吹埋嚟已經好似十號風球咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁遇著真正我地本身認知嘅十號風球係喺會冚球鏟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個文明係fail 嘅話係咪證明有腦都無用 本身嘅體型都好重要？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"樓主可能要搞清楚先後因果<br />\n人類文明係因為現有物理特性所以發展出現世文明產物 例如高樓 獨立供冷 室內照明等等<br />\n如果開波果下係蟻咁既size 衣食住行既模式會同宜家好唔同<br />\n<br />\n答番你問題<br />\n樓，一般電子用品得。但去到比IC更上一個級，例如10nm, 7nm做core tech應該暫時唔得"},{"pid":"6e8191b8617cb23306dabdbc7097ab191e4ad62f","tid":1179230,"uid":60109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"你連生物上既限制都假設無問題<br />\n我覺得物理上仲容易解決<br />\n反正而家個世界都係細細個人大大部機器"},{"pid":"163d7a4d67c1ca05d5e87e34d16ce2abc2932b1d","tid":1179230,"uid":31215,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a5263a3b22ac2904648e3b65fae0fa8e2971bbd8","tid":1179230,"uid":183898,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"aea0ffeebc4dd403749305c67a57f946e46ba281","tid":1179230,"uid":22566,"like":615,"dislike":7,"score":608,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"大膽啲諗 依家會唔會已經係呢個情況"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T22:50:16.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係，可能螞蟻本身都以為自己好大隻，有自己既文明，而人本身都係咁諗，大家都察覺唔到高於自己文明既存在。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"根本就係<br />\n蟻住蟻穴<br />\n自己有成個城<br />\n出面有個地球係未知<br />\n地球外更有完全唔知嘅宇宙<br />\n<br />\n人住地球<br />\n出面有個宇宙係未知<br />\n宇宙外會唔會有更多平行時空重重宇宙嗰啲對人類都係唔知"},{"pid":"51ea67e973fc0d026fb788b871d180ce3e54315b","tid":1179230,"uid":48106,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"845ee76eeed074c4ed3a1d2241453782531d6843","tid":1179230,"uid":17322,"like":12,"dislike":56,"score":-44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八"},{"pid":"d29fc107d5cbc9d24449d0674c5c10fdd057ed58","